        "text": "PR #42 (repo-pulse article output) merged 48h after the May-17 skill-freshness audit flagged the gap. Step 7 added to `skills/repo-pulse/SKILL.md` to emit `articles/repo-pulse-${today}.md` with the canonical fields 5 consumer skills (operator-scorecard, thread-formatter, star-momentum-alert, show-hn-draft, skill-freshness) had been silently falling back to memory/logs parsers for. Second consecutive self-correction cycle merged <48h.",
        "variant": "body"
